<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3876637>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Geelus dundraad gen.n. & sp.n., habitus, dorsally. A. Male, Uitsig, Rooibos Tea; B. Female, Groenkol, Rooibos Tea; C. Male, Jamaka, on Aspalathus; D. Female, Jamaka, Aspalathus; E. Male, Koelenhof specimen; F. Female, Klipheuwel; G. Male, Wiedouw specimen, on Diosma; H. Male, Citrusdal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3876637/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3876643>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Geelus dundraad gen.n. & sp.n., male head, wings and genitalia, line drawings. A. Head, dorsally. B. Face; C. Head, laterally; D. Tegmina; E. Hind wing; F. Aedeagus, ventrally; G. Aedeagus, laterally; H. Connective; I. Abdominal apodemes; J. Style; K. Subgenital plate; L. Genital capsule, dorsally; M. Style, apophysis, laterally; N. Style, apophysis, dorsally; O. Genital capsule, laterally." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3876643/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3876647>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Geelus dundraad gen.n. & sp.n., male and female genitalia, line drawings. A. Aedeagus, ventrally; B. Aedeagus, laterally; C. Connective; D. Style; E. Genital capsule, laterally; F. Pygofer process, caudally, dorsal orientation; G. Pygofer process, caudally, mediodorsal orientation; H. Subgenital plate; I. Valvifer 1, laterally; J. Sternite 7, Wiedouw specimen, on Diosma, Wiborgia and other plants, Boskloof; K. Sternite 7, Groenkol, on Rooibos Tea; L. Sternite 7, Koelenhof specimen; M. Sternite 7, Muldersvlei specimen; N. Sternite 7, Piketberg specimen; O. Sternite 7, Wiedouw specimen, on Passerina and Aspalathus, Uitsig." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3876647/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

